License: GPL (>= 2)
Description: Robust quadratic discriminant analysis including cross-validation. The Minimum Covariance Determinant does most of the job. References: Friedman J., Hastie T. and Tibshirani R. (2009). The elements of statistical learning, 2nd edition. Springer, Berlin. <doi:10.1007/978-0-387-84858-7>. 
